overview: Terminus: All Roads Lead Here is the first event from Terminus Pro-wrestling Promotion, which is created by former ROH wrestlers. The event will take place on January 16 from Salvation Army Kroc in Atlanta, GA.  The main event will feature Jonathan Gresham vs Josh Alexander for ROH Original World Championship. The co-main event will be Baron Black vs Bandido for ROH World Championship. Several ROH, IMPACT Wrestling and Independent wrestlers will appear on the show.
title: Terminus: All Roads Lead Here
